# Task Plugins

The Task extension endpoint allows plugin authors to extenGoCD to send notifications about builds over various channels.

If you're looking to start away with a basic template for notification plugins, we recommend forking this [github repository](https://github.com/gocd-contrib/task-skeleton-plugin).

